	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Fallraen, a town at the foot of Mt. Elspen. \nNormally a harsh & unforgiving land, things are even worse than normal this summer. \nAn unseasonable Blizzard has swept in and destroyed the Spring crops and famine is biting at the gates of the town.\nIsolated and facing starvation, the people of Fallraen have no one they can turn to.\nIs there a connection with the call of the Priests for the reunification of the Stones?\nOr is it just one coincidence amongst the many difficulties besieging the Kingdom?";
