	{
	order = 0;
		//sample = s_v_greet_male_allochap;
	screen_text = "Master Lagreth is going to have my hide! I borrowed a stack of books, and lent two out to some friends. But now, I don't remember to whom I lent them! Priest Lagreth forbids me to leave while he is absent, but I am sure he will find them missing when he returns. I've been searching everywhere but I can't find them.  Might you have a few minutes to ask around town for me?";
