	{
		screen_text = "Please don't bother me, I'm walking around trying to keep warm. I've frostbite on places you wouldn't imagine and until recently my lips were stuck together and I couldn't even talk! And this Nice Guy came around to try to chat me up too, then left in a huff when I couldn't reply to him. He was so handsome too. What's a lass to do, huh.";
